    "Unknown": "They that walk by sense, are ready to say of the unseen Jesus `[char_Jesus_Ref]`, as the people did of Moses `[char_Moses_Exo_2]` when he tarried in the mount upon their errand, We wot not what is become of him, and therefore up, make us gods, the world a god, the belly a god, any thing but him that should be."
